attributes.mlflow.spanInputs: {"prompt": "Configure model-driven telemetry for EVPN on IOS XR with server 10.10.10.10:57000, tcp, sample interval 30000ms."}
attributes.mlflow.spanOutputs:
"telemetry model-driven
 sensor-group EVPN
  sensor-path Cisco-IOS-XR-evpn-oper:evpn/active/instances/instance
 !
 destination-group DG-GRPC
  address-family ipv4
   destination 10.10.10.10
    port 57000
    encoding self-describing-gpb
    protocol grpc no-tls
 !
 subscription SUB-EVPN
  sensor-group-id EVPN sample-interval 30000
  destination-group-id DG-GRPC
 !"
